{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: '\\\\601D源黑体cn', 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">一、理清老板的真实需求</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">公司当前形势如何？最近是否有新动向？</span></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">向做过类似任务的前辈求教。</span></span></font></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: '\\\\601D源黑体cn', 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">之前老板表扬过的报告是如何的？</span></span><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><br></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">老板，你觉得我这个报告那里写得不满意？你想要看到怎样的报告？</span></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">老板对报告批评的点集中在那里。</span></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">二、老板的需求还可以怎么实现&amp;我怎么帮对方实现</span></span></font></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">如果是行业整体分析，是否调研一下，购买专业人员的报告。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">如果对报告样式不美观，是否学习下可视化，让报告更易读</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑; font-size: 0.947rem;\">老板平时喜欢的样式是怎样的？之前表扬过的报告是如何的？</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7369,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491564211000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"和老板沟通，从计划的结构、表现形式看有哪些重点提升项","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7351,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491545890000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p>当你觉察到，对方声称的需求有可能不是真实需求时，思考三个问题：</p><p>1）对方真正的需求是什么——为什么老板会需要这个报告？这个报告是用在什么地方？这个报告是要解决什么问题？</p><p>2）对方的需求还可以通过什么方式实现——除了做这份报告之外，还有什么办法可以解决老板的需求？</p><p>3）我可以怎么帮助对方实现——如果有别的方式，那么我可以做一些什么来帮助他解决？</p><p>为了验证对方的真实需求，可以：</p><p>1）注意观察细节——老板最近最烦恼的事情是什么？</p><p>2）侧面了解——从老板的助理等更近亲的人那边打听消息</p><p>3）直接向对方提问——这个报告的问题在哪里？老板需要帮助解决的是什么？<br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7298,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491482337000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"程然","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibeXpgwkiaTloWbvWZibHU3ulLlIhhE6iaIiazJaXkXaYkTTbdwvhdOM7cvxOoQpCxud7DYns8icjZDZ7w/0","content":"1.仔细观察。老板是在什么情况下把报告打回来的?有没有其他人员对报告提出问题?老板把报告打回来时说了什么？<div><br><div>2.直接提问。这个报告问题出在哪里?有哪方面需要完善?</div></div><div><br></div><div>3.侧面了解。通过老员工或者以前的相关报告，了解老板的标准和要求。通过相关业务部门，了解该报告运用的项目进度如何?有何变化？</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7223,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491361774000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>1、询问老板的秘书或者助理，老板对于报告的 <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">真实需求是什么？</span></p><p>2、注意了解老板最近最关注的是哪一方面的内容？</p><p>3、老板心情较好且较空闲时，询问老板的真实需求是什么？ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5867,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491308846000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"薛定谔的猫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7Ib4ia2sVL55YvGrTiayCMcic3HV27qHddTlOV8oBEfiaOTCkRqyNqG119jQ0umRddvUoCL0uEmYJpUTRGaibS8S8ToJdjNjf2Mls8/0","content":"<p>1.重新分析报告对象的特征，找到公司感兴趣的点</p><p>2.回顾自己的报告，对比是否是根据这些特征所做</p><p>3.直接询问老板所关注的内容</p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7196,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491308757000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"通过跟老板沟通，要知道老板先要看到什么，使自己的认知方面在老板那里，沟通我的问题在那里，要解决什么问题，干什么东西，方向在哪儿，老板要的不是数字，看到你的改变在哪里，结果是什么。问题在那里。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7190,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491304715000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"灿灿","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJrWntUHNk0zHK1D4Erd9HKhAcDtR33woSI7GNbwLt73SrysUaw3L8spMJicd8quTia0pEUpia9JDtkGJVNX9lAkp5/0","content":"<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 48px; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">1）<span style='font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">对方真正的需求是什么；</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">小明通过直接向老板提问寻找真正需求。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">老板我的报告是用来干什么用的？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">老板我的报告有问题，是哪方面的问题。是格式不对吗，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">word</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">还是我的内容有问题，不够结构化？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">我报告里面的数据有错误？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">注意观察细节：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">看到老板匆匆浏览，不是针对某个内容仔细看，说明是整体上不满意，排除数据错误等细节。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">侧面了解：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">老板要参加公司的销售大会，准备在会议做演讲，告诉产品本季度的销售指标，取得的成功及不足的地方。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">通过产品了解到他们一般需要了解那些内容。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 48px; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">2）<span style='font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">对方的需求还可以通过什么方式实现；</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">格式，演讲用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">产品部门角度，讲给产品同事用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">数据可视化，让参加会议的一目了然。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 48px; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">3）<span style='font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">我可以怎么帮助对方实现</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">Word</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">格式修改成</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">。给老板开会</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">演讲用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">压缩内容，提炼</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">要点。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-size: 9pt;\">PPT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">内容修改成以产品线为角度阐述销售业绩，代替以前以地区业绩为角度。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 11px 24px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">数据可视化，减少表哥，增加图形透视。</span></p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7125,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491193338000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLDqSSXIAzKphVGZMibQL8RZHItR7wlTetH47SYQgiasgxu/0","content":"<p>1. 回想前几次老板打回报告时，都说了些什么。找出共性特征，以及这些信息中是否隐藏了某些信息。</p><p>2. 找做出的报告得到老板赏识的同事聊一聊，看一看他们的报告，得知老板对他们的报告的具体好评信息后，通过对比，从侧面了解老板的着重点及真正需求。</p><p>3. 直接向老板提问，关于报告的相关信息，诸如：背景、目的、相关方、时间节点、可用资源、要达到的效果等。</p><p>4. 在确认老板等真正需求后，思考自己可以通过哪些方式实现，我又可以提供些什么。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7112,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491144646000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"奥古斯塔","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6ic8hPq6WhALCpZNd5Licic1qwBQCtt6DFicMG7jozs0rIn4eD4Fic3RKMklqPNRSeRZiawJYmYPn4w7vpSPz5FWIpG5l/0","content":"1.观察细节：琢磨老板的意见和神情，大概是对自己报告哪部分开始变脸色？老板最不认同哪一点？\n2.侧面了解：重新看自己的报告，和同事交流一下；问老板：是不是报告不够详细还是用词不够严谨？\n3.正面了解：问老板：你想要达到什么效果？对报告有什么不满意的地方？我应该注重哪部分的修改？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7009,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490962636000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"思考：\n1.老板想要改善会议流程的真正原因是什么？难道只是提高会议效率吗？\n老板的真正需求一般都是公司利润的提高。\n通过观察老板在看到哪一部分时不满意，来猜测；同时侧面了解最近公司发生的可能影响老板的重要事情，是否有业务下滑，客户减少等情况；还可以直接问老板哪个地方做的不够好，来推断出老板的真正需求。\n2.老板的需求还可以通过提升业务量，扩大公司经营范围等等方式实现。\n3.我可以在报告中深挖改善会议流程与这些关键业务之间的关系，譬如通过改善流程能减少会议时间，提高工作效率，提升业务量，拓展新的市场。以此方式来满足老板的需求。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6871,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490962470000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"史自力","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8CYiaFWibYsq0TUGzGLj6UOnQ45ibnxbp7iahCxUOOANST662hUnQyfQYXKPdy0O5N6NOriaaj7UGVhy/0","content":"询问老板哪里令老板不满意？不满意的原因是什么？他想要一个什么样的报告，这份报告包含哪些需求，什么格式写出来更合适？什么时间完成！","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6825,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490884691000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType